 bash-completion
Description: Minimal desktop environment for budgie-remix
 Installs a minimal set of budgie-remix packages, both essential dependencies
 as well as recommended packages and applications.  The package is useful
 for system builders who want budgie-desktop without the full set of 
 applications recommended in budgie-remix
 
Package: budgie-desktop-common
Architecture: all
Section: misc
Depends: 
    ${misc:Depends}
Description: Common budgie-remix desktop components
 budgie-desktop common components i.e.
 gsettings overrides
 make QT apps look like GTK apps
